latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#padherlife is an everteen initiative to support Covid pandemic affected women and families. Let's join hands and empower our Indian household women by providing them the opportunity to learn and earn at the same time. 
everteen is coming forward to provide financial aid of up to Rs. 50,000 through its Neem and Safflower sanitary pads. The whole purpose behind running this exhilarating campaign is to contribute a little in enhancing the engagement of women in economic activities especially after the COVID -19 crisis.
The needy women/families can redeem this financial support by visiting www.sheneedspad.com and by filling in all the relevant details required.
Please share this message, video and help spread the word about this life-changing initiative as much as possible.
